

Here are some sample **Delivery Manager / Senior Manager** level interview questions (for a banking / IT-services environment) tailored for BNY Mellon (USA) and for a client engagement via Mphasis (India). Alongside, Iâ€™ve given tips / sample structuring of good answers. You can adapt your answers to your own experience.

  
